verbose_text: We have adjusted this function with variable prefactors to the Boys-Bernardi CP energy of the S6634 noncovalent dimers (see below) for functionals with varying amount of Fock exchange (PBE : 0%, B3LYP : 20%, PBEh-3c : 42%, HF : 100%) and increasing BS size (MINIX, def2-SV (P), def2-TZVP, def2-QZVP).
